text.tspan: RFC2474 DiffServ redesign of ToS/TC fields

tspan.tspan: A replacement header field, called the DS field, is defined, which is
intended to supersede the existing definitions of the IPv4 TOS octet
[RFC791] and the IPv6 Traffic Class octet [IPv6].
